--- !u!114 &1499817050
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 1499817048}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 48fdfcc8a67199e4aa51c8e7b7b14715, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::WitcherRightVersion.Dialogue.DialogueInteractable
  displayName: Elsa Cherntravka
  interactionPrompt: Talk
  startNodeId: start
  returnToElderNodeId: 
  completedQuestNodeId: 
  dialogueNodes:
  - Id: start
    SpeakerName: Elsa Cherntravka
    Body: Do not draw steel. If Voytsekh sent you, he sent you to kill the only witness
      who still remembers the first version.
    Choices:
    - Text: Tell me what the mirror did.
      NextNodeId: mirror
      FlagToSet: 
      QuestAction: start_exile
      ClosesDialogue: 0
    - Text: I will protect you from the elder.
      NextNodeId: protected
      FlagToSet: ElsaProtected
      QuestAction: elsa_protected
      ClosesDialogue: 0
    - Text: The village wants you taken in.
      NextNodeId: betrayed
      FlagToSet: ElsaBetrayed
      QuestAction: elsa_betrayed
      ClosesDialogue: 0
    - Text: Later.
      NextNodeId: 
      FlagToSet: 
      QuestAction: 
      ClosesDialogue: 1
  - Id: mirror
    SpeakerName: Elsa Cherntravka
    Body: Orten made them a kinder memory. The girl became a witch. The killers became
      saviors. The swamp became a grave that could still speak.
    Choices:
    - Text: Help me reach the tower.
      NextNodeId: protected
      FlagToSet: ElsaProtected
      QuestAction: elsa_protected
      ClosesDialogue: 0
    - Text: I need proof, not faith.
      NextNodeId: 
      FlagToSet: 
      QuestAction: 
      ClosesDialogue: 1
  - Id: protected
    SpeakerName: Elsa Cherntravka
    Body: Then take the reed charm. It will not open the tower alone, but the ruins
      will know you came for the buried version.
    Choices:
    - Text: I will use it.
      NextNodeId: 
      FlagToSet: TowerRouteOpened
      QuestAction: tower_route_opened
      ClosesDialogue: 1
  - Id: betrayed
    SpeakerName: Elsa Cherntravka
    Body: Of course. Villages are very good at hiring clean hands for dirty endings.
    Choices:
    - Text: This ends cleanly.
      NextNodeId: 
      FlagToSet: MayorSupported
      QuestAction: elsa_betrayed
      ClosesDialogue: 1
